sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent as 🤖 AI Agent
    participant MCP as 🖥️ MCP Server
    participant Handler as ⚙️ Handler
    participant Validator as ✅ InputValidator
    participant Service as 🔍 AnalysisService
    participant Parser as 🌳 TreeSitterParser
    participant Graph as 🕸️ PetGraphStore
    participant Safety as 🛡️ SafetyGate
    participant Strategy as 🔨 RenameStrategy
    participant VFS as 💾 VirtualFileSystem

    Agent->>MCP: safe_refactor(rename, symbol="foo", new_name="bar")
    
    MCP->>Handler: handle_safe_refactor(params)
    Handler->>Validator: validate_path(file_path)
    Validator-->>Handler: PathValid
    
    Handler->>Service: rename_symbol(command)
    
    Service->>Safety: check_risk_level(symbol)
    Safety-->>Service: RiskLevel::Medium
    
    Service->>Graph: find_all_references(symbol)
    Graph-->>Service: Vec&lt;Location&gt;
    
    Service->>Parser: parse_file(file_path)
    Parser-->>Service: Tree
    
    Service->>Strategy: prepare_edits(symbol, new_name, tree)
    Strategy-->>Service: Vec&lt;TextEdit&gt;
    
    Service->>VFS: apply_edits(edits)
    VFS-->>Service: VirtualFileSystem(updated)
    
    Service->>Parser: validate_syntax(vfs)
    Parser-->>Service: SyntaxValid
    
    Service-->>Handler: RefactorPreviewDto { changes, preview }
    Handler-->>MCP: { jsonrpc, result: preview }
    MCP-->>Agent: JSON-RPC Response

    Note over Agent,VFS: Preview Mode - No changes applied yet
    
    Agent->>MCP: safe_refactor(apply=true)
    MCP->>Service: apply_rename(changes)
    Service->>Graph: update_symbol(old, new)
    Service-->>Agent: { success: true, applied: 5 }
